; Regression test for issue #1091: Unicode white space on empty lines confuses ledger (BZ#1091)
; https://github.com/ledger/ledger/issues/1091
;
; A line containing only a Unicode non-breaking space (U+00A0) should
; be treated as an empty line, but instead triggers a directive error.

2024/01/01 First
    Expenses:Food    $10.00
    Assets:Cash
 
2024/01/02 Second
    Expenses:Food    $5.00
    Assets:Cash

test bal -> 1
__ERROR__
While parsing file "$FILE", line 10:
Error: Directive ' ' requires an argument
end test
